```class Solution {
    public boolean checkRecord(String s) {
        int absent = 0, late = 0;
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == 'A') absent++;
            if (c == 'L') late = late == 2 ? 0 : late + 1;
        }
        return absent < 2 && late < 3;
    }
}```
